


<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>OTP Verification</title>
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: #f6f6f6;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        }
        table {
            border-collapse: collapse;
        }
        .container {
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 860px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }
        h1 {
            font-size: 20px;
            color: #313131;
            margin: 0 0 10px;
        }
        p {
            color: #313131;
            font-size: 14px;
            line-height: 1.5;
            margin: 8px 0;
        }
        .otp {
            font-size: 28px;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #000;
            margin: 20px 0;
            padding: 12px 20px;
            border-radius: 5px;
            border: 1px solid #313131;
            background-color: #fff;
            text-align: center;
        }
        .footer {
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #777;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 15px 20px;
        }
        .logo{
            display: block;
            height: auto;
            max-width: 100%;
            position: relative;
            top: -5px;
        }
        .dogs {
            display: block;
            height: auto;
            max-width: 100%;
            position: relative;
            top:25px !important;
        }
        a.button {
            width:calc(100% - 65px);display:block; padding: 12px 30px; font-size: 16px;background-color: #ffa54b; color: #fff; text-decoration: none; font-weight: 300; border-radius: 6px; text-align: center;
        }

        table.new {
            margin-top: 20px;
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
            border: 1px solid #eaeaea; /* ðŸ‘ˆ outer outline */
        }

        table.new th,
        table.new td {
            padding: 12px;
            text-align: left;
            color: #313131;
            font-size: 14px;

            border-bottom: 1px solid #eaeaea; /* ðŸ‘ˆ only row divider */
        }

        table.new th:last-child,
        table.new td:last-child {
            border-right: none; /* remove extra right border */
        }
        table.new th {
            font-weight: bold;
            color: #313131;
        }

        @media only screen and (max-width: 600px) {
            h1 { font-size: 16px !important; }
            p { font-size: 12px !important; }
            .otp { font-size: 18px !important; padding: 10px !important; }
            .logo { width: 40px !important; }
            .dogs { width: 140px !important; top:31px !important;  position: relative}
            .content { padding: 15px !important; }
            a.button {
                font-size: 12px;
                padding: 10px 20px;
                width:calc(100% - 50px);
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>



<table role="presentation" class="container" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%">
    <!-- Header -->
    <tr>
        <td style="padding:0; margin:0;">
            <table role="presentation" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="100%"
                   style="background:linear-gradient(90deg,#fce3df 0%,#e7f2f7 100%); min-height: 180px">
                <tr>
                    <td style="padding:20px;">
                        <table role="presentation" width="100%">
                            <tr>
                                <td valign="top">
                                    <img src="https://app-dev.project-name.project-name.io/app-logo.png" alt="logo" class="logo" width="55" />
                                </td>
                                <td align="right" valign="bottom">
                                    <img src="https://app-dev.project-name.project-name.io/invite-e-t.png"
                                         alt="Puppies illustration" class="dogs" width="200" />
                                </td>
                            </tr>
                        </table>
                    </td>
                </tr>
            </table>
        </td>
    </tr>

    <!--  Content -->
    <tr>
        <td class="content" style="padding:25px;">
            <h1>Shortlisted for Event | Invitation</h1>
            <p>Hello {{name}},</p>
            <p>Youâ€™re on the shortlist for {{eventName}} .. nice work! <br/>
                Your golden ticket (okay, itâ€™s a QR code) is attached below. Flash it at the entrance and let the good times begin.</p>
            <p>To get started, please log into your account by clicking the button below:</p>
            <a class="button" href="{{googleWalletLink}}" target="_blank"
               style="">
                Add to Google Wallet
            </a>
            <br>
            <a class="button" href="{{appleWalletLink}}" target="_blank"
               style="">
                Add to Apple Wallet
            </a>

            <table class="new">
                <thead>
                <tr>
                    <th>Event Name</th>
                    <th>Type</th>
                    <th>Date</th>
                    <th>Application Date</th>
                    <th>Address</th>
                </tr>
                </thead>
                <tbody>
                <tr>
                    <td>{{eventName}}</td>
                    <td>{{locationType}}</td>
                    <td>{{startTime}}</td>
                    <td>{{createdAt}}</td>
                    <td>{{locationValue}}</td>
                </tr>
                </tbody>
            </table>
            <p>If you have any questions or need support, feel free to reply to this email or contact us at <a href="mailto:support@theproject-name.com" style="color: #313131">support@theproject-name.com</a></p>

            <p>Stay Awesome,<br/><strong>Team The project-name</strong></p>
        </td>
    </tr>

</table>
</body>
</html>
